  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/hypervisor\/3181560-vm-capabilities\ncrawled: 2026-03-11T08:42:16Z\n---\n\n# VM Capabilities\n\n**API Collection**\n\nAn enumeration that describes the capabilities of the system.\n\n## Constants\n\n- **HV_CAP_ADDRSPACEMAX**: A value that indicates the maximum number of available address spaces.\n- **HV_CAP_VCPUMAX**: A value that indicates the maximum number of available vCPUs.\n\n## Enumerations\n\n- **VM Creation Options**: Constants that describe the creation options for a virtual machine.\n- **hv_cache_type_t**: The structure that describes an instruction or data cache element.\n- **hv_boot_state**\n- **hv_apic_ctrl_t**\n- **hv_apic_intr_trigger_t**\n- **hv_apic_lvt_flavor_t**\n- **hv_gic_distributor_reg_t**\n- **hv_gic_icc_reg_t**\n- **hv_gic_ich_reg_t**\n- **hv_gic_icv_reg_t**\n- **hv_gic_intid_t**\n- **hv_gic_msi_reg_t**\n- **hv_gic_redistributor_reg_t**\n- **hv_sme_p_reg_t**\n- **hv_sme_z_reg_t**\n\n",
